title: Sweet Liquor Numbs the Pain
description: We have some fun Disney facts you probably have never heard, Dave tells us about the saddest Super Bowl party, we play "Spelling Super Bowl" where we try to spell MN/WI cities and if we get them wrong we have to take a shot of something that would be at a Super Bowl party, War of the Roses, and more!
